### 2. Domain 모듈의 Chat 관련 Entity/Repository

**`/domain/` 모듈에서 Chat 관련 파일** (가이드 기반)

```
domain/
├── src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/
│   ├── entity/
│   │   ├── ChatRoomEntity.kt
│   │   ├── ChatMessageEntity.kt
│   │   ├── ChatParticipantEntity.kt
│   │   └── ChatSettingEntity.kt
│   └── repository/
│       ├── ChatRoomRepository.kt
│       ├── ChatMessageRepository.kt
│       ├── ChatParticipantRepository.kt
│       └── ChatSettingRepository.kt
└── build.gradle.kts
```

**예상 Entity 구조** (가이드 기반):

```kotlin
// ChatRoomEntity.kt
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "chat", name = "chat_room")
class ChatRoomEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val name: String,
    val description: String?,
    val roomType: Int,  // 1:1, 그룹
    val createdBy: String,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)

// ChatMessageEntity.kt
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "chat", name = "chat_message")
class ChatMessageEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val chatRoomId: String,
    val userId: String,
    val content: String,
    val messageType: Int,  // TEXT, IMAGE, etc.

    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JoinColumn(name = "chat_room_id", referencedColumnName = "id")
    val chatRoom: ChatRoomEntity? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

**Repository 인터페이스**:

```kotlin
interface ChatRoomRepository : JpaRepository<ChatRoomEntity, String> {
    fun findByCreatedBy(userId: String): List<ChatRoomEntity>
    fun findByRoomType(roomType: Int): List<ChatRoomEntity>
}

interface ChatMessageRepository : JpaRepository<ChatMessageEntity, String> {
    fun findByChatRoomId(chatRoomId: String): List<ChatMessageEntity>
    fun findByChatRoomIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc(chatRoomId: String): List<ChatMessageEntity>
}
```

**Catalog 정보** (entity-skill 가이드):
- `chat` 카탈로그: `chat_room` 테이블

